\v 1 N\nd kosi\nd*, inhliziyo yami kayikhukhumali\x + Hlab. 138.6.\x*, lamehlo ami kawaphakami\x + 2 Sam. 6.22. Hlab. 101.5.\x*, njalo kangihambi ezintweni ezinkulu lezintweni ezimangalisayo kakhulu kimi\x + Jer. 45.5. Roma 12.16.\x*.
\v 2 Sibili ngichumisile ngathulisa umphefumulo wami, njengolunyuliweyo kunina; umphefumulo wami unjengolunyuliweyo phakathi kwami\x + Mat. 18.3.\x*.
\v 3 UIsrayeli kathembele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kusukela khathesi kuze kube laphakade\x + Hlab. 130.7.\x*.
